name: ergo
description: A lightweight php5 library for request/response routing, controllers and http interaction.

commit.message:
Merge pull request #23 from 99designs/v2-remove-type-hints

V2: remove addFilter() type hints

Remove type-hints from addFilter()

- \Ergo\Http\Client::addFilter()
- \Ergo\Routing\RequestFilter::addFilter()

This permits other libraries like 99designs/relax to provide filters
which work with ergo v1 and v2.

Merge pull request #21 from 99designs/expose-route-parameters

Expose route parameter names via Route::getParameterNames()
Expose route parameter names

Revive old controller classes for improved backwards compatibility
Revive old controller classes for improved backwards compatibility

Restore the old array access interface for RouteMatch
Restore the old array access interface for RouteMatch

PSR-3 logging

PSR3 exception logging
Fix cibuild
Fix test

Commerce updates

Added suffix parameter to \Ergo\Routing\ControllerDirectory

Updates to make commerce work with latest Ergo

Provide more detail in exceptions resulting from curl errors
Provide more detail in exceptions resulting from curl errors

Only allow http and https for outgoing connections
Excercise request creation in tests for ipFamily
Remove extra dollar
Merge tag 'v2.2.1'

Add setIPFamily

Add setIPFamily

Show sample output from phpunit
Use phpunit for CI
Add composer.lockwq
Convert tests from SimpleTest to PHPUnit
Convert tests from SimpleTest to PHPUnit
Convert tests from SimpleTest to PHPUnit

Use single quotes for readable namespaces

Merge pull request #11 from 99designs/features/nullrequest

Implement NullRequest for Console invocations
Implement NullRequest for Console invocations
Add ErrorContext::get to allow easier interrogation of the error context

Use TIMEOUT_MS over TIMEOUT inside curl

This fixes an issue with curl's internal use of SIGALRM and dns
resolution, documented here:

http://ravidhavlesha.wordpress.com/2012/01/08/curl-timeout-problem-and-solution/
Fix bug in RouteMap::parameter
Flip cibuild executable bit
Create a cibuild script to ease automated testing

Create a getBaseUrl method on Client
Create a getBaseUrl method on Client
Added option to set HTTP client connect timeout

Merge pull request #7 from 99designs/request-params

Fix bug handling empty query string
Fix bug handling empty query string

Merge pull request #6 from 99designs/request-params

Add method to merge query parameters in URL
Use QueryString class for query string manipulations
New method to add query parameters to URL
Add optional ability for FileConfig::loadFile to merge configuration recursively
Fix bug where multiple params are parsed incorrectly
Add autostart() for lazy-starting Applications
Support either/or options in Options parser

Merge pull request #4 from 99designs/composer-dev-deps

Use Composer to manage development dependencies
Fix Composer link in README.md
Use Composer to manage development dependencies
Magic method such that Ergo::application()->llamas() looks up 'llamas' in Registry.
Changed composer vendor to 99designs
Replaced Pundlefile with Composer file
Options now uses a correctly typed NULL when given param=null

Merge pull request #3 from 99designs/dynamic-landing-pages-template-sinamt

Support for Route subclassing
Re-factored named route lookup to improve performance.
Added Ergo\Console\Options::fetch() for neater default arg handling
Fixed comment typo
DRYed up some route matching code

Router now stores custom route instances separately to 'standard'
routes, to improve ability to cache in the future.

Replaced _isMatch() with _getMatches(), removing need for _pathMatches
class property.
Merge branch 'master', remote branch 'origin' into dynamic-landing-pages-template-sinamt
Test for setting a custom Route in the Router.
Adding ability to directly connect to customised Routes.
Fixed Ergo\Console\Options throwing InvalidArgumentException

Merge branch 'simple-request-response'

* simple-request-response:
  Request & Response now support returning simplified versions of themselves
Request & Response now support returning simplified versions of themselves
Provide a hostname for PHP web errors.
Added random number generation for controlling random numbers in test cases
Provide a hostname for PHP console errors.
Added test coverage to setHttpProxy, setHttpAuth & setTimeout methods on Http\Client
Fixed a bug in Ergo\Http\Client::setHttpAuth
Added static constructor to Ergo http url

Merge pull request #1 from 99designs/http-transport

Extracted Http\Transport from Http\Client
Extracted Http\Transport from Http\Client
Initialise headers to empty array in RequestFactory
Introduced an ErrorContext object to allow for easier managing for error context data
Removed method existance check in Ergo static dispatch

Merge branch 'v2.x'

* v2.x:
  Fixed a bug in RouteMatch::hasMetadata, always returned false
  Final fixes for v2
  Initial implementation of middleware
  Added metadata to routes, returned in matches. Changed how redirects and aliaseswork, simpler now.
  Revised readme
  Removed Pake as a dependancy
  Updated runtests.php to use new vendor path for simpletest
  Added a Pundlefile for checking documentation
  Updated readme to reflect project changes
  Fixed a bug where lookup closure trumped trigger in the Registry
  Various namespace and 5.3 specific fixes
  Updated application to support controller and router
  Implemented ControllerDirectory
  Replaced filter chains with a filtered controller
  Added custom prefix callbacks for controller resolution
  Skeleton router, redirect and resolver code
  Renamed RouteMap to Router
  Migrated to use PHP 5.3 packages and closures where appropriate
Fixed a bug in RouteMatch::hasMetadata, always returned false
Final fixes for v2

Merge branch 'master' into v2.x

* master:
  Revert "Replace backslash with forwardslash when a namespace is supplied"
  Replace backslash with forwardslash when a namespace is supplied
  Added support for namespaces to ergo classloader
  Added a short-hand syntax for Options::value() and fixed bug where ! specifier wasn't implemented.
  Changed the shutdown function to be static
  Ergo_Http_Client post() and put() methods accept a Content-Type.
  Ergo_Http_Status has isOk() method to check status code is 200.
  Ergo_Application::setDateTime uses constant from Ergo not Spf.
  ConsolerErrorHandler still works if output buffering is enabled
  Fixed mis-named class file; Errors => Error.

Conflicts:
	classes/Ergo/Application.php
	classes/Ergo/ClassLoader.php
	classes/Ergo/Http/Client.php
	classes/Ergo/Http/Status.php

Revert "Replace backslash with forwardslash when a namespace is supplied"

This reverts commit e99dd584fb68b634a346323b31b2465dee98dd39.
Replace backslash with forwardslash when a namespace is supplied
Added support for namespaces to ergo classloader
Added a short-hand syntax for Options::value() and fixed bug where ! specifier wasn't implemented.
Changed the shutdown function to be static

Ergo_Http_Client post() and put() methods accept a Content-Type.

Without setting a Content-Type, cURL will set it to
application/x-www-form-urlencoded for these requests.
Ergo_Http_Status has isOk() method to check status code is 200.
Ergo_Application::setDateTime uses constant from Ergo not Spf.
ConsolerErrorHandler still works if output buffering is enabled
Initial implementation of middleware
Added metadata to routes, returned in matches. Changed how redirects and aliaseswork, simpler now.
Revised readme
Removed Pake as a dependancy
Updated runtests.php to use new vendor path for simpletest
Added a Pundlefile for checking documentation
Updated readme to reflect project changes
Fixed mis-named class file; Errors => Error.
Fixed a bug where lookup closure trumped trigger in the Registry
Various namespace and 5.3 specific fixes
Updated application to support controller and router
Implemented ControllerDirectory
Replaced filter chains with a filtered controller
Added custom prefix callbacks for controller resolution
Skeleton router, redirect and resolver code
Renamed RouteMap to Router
Migrated to use PHP 5.3 packages and closures where appropriate
Added a log level to the constructor of the FileLogger
Fixed FileConfig for varnames of $config
FileConfig.php no longer triggers notices if optional config files are missing
Added special cases to error handlers for when headers have already been sent.
Added a method to test if an application instance is started.
Cleared up $_SERVER pollution in unit test
Changed HTTP_HOST to SERVER_NAME as the former includes a port.
Fixed bug in options parsing related to flag values that started with a dash.
Made config objects iteratable
Support set() on FileConfig
Converted exceptions to messages retrieved via errors() in Options.
Removed syntactic sugar from Options parser, use value() and values()
Refactored options, added errors() method for validation
Added support for options with dashes in them in the Options parser
Added a getUrlForFragment method to Ergo_Http_Url
Refactored logging system to be more chainable
fixed issue where changing scheme for a relative url would fail
Url::getUrlForScheme() will attempt to set the port to the default for target scheme. Test coverage of said method added.
Added support for --arg=value arguments in the Options parser.
Added a requestTime var to the http client for monitoring time taken.
Added http authentication
RequestFactory uses scheme from requestUri if scheme header is missing.
Added support for setSchemeHeader to the RequestFactory.
Fixed typo in RouteMap
Added an entry method to the RouteMap
Added tags to route map match and entry
Made it possible to get prototype logger from logger factory

Call to Ergo::stop() is now optional.

Ergo::stop is now called via a shutdown function
The result is that the worker and scripts will clean up temp files better.
Fixed warning in RequestTest
Updated runtests.php to use Options parser
Updated RoutedController->connect to use new parameters.
Fixed bug in Application->setDateTime()
Breaking change to API, routemap now requires one call to map per entry.
Fixed bug where arguments with dashes broke the Options parser.
Returns default values for missing parameters
WebErrorHandler now flushes the output buffer when sending an error for PHP 5.3 compatibility
Added a basic command line options parser
ErrorProxy and StackTraceLogger have updated error constant to string mappings.
Added an array based Logger class
Fixed error proxy so it still shows an error even without an error handler.
Fixed code example in README; passed application to Ergo::start().
Further readme updating.
Updated readme.
Added an MIT license file and a README for opensourcing.
Added a test runner and patched a test to support latest simpletest.
Added Ergo::register() method.
Moved classname=>file logic into template method in ClassLoader.
Added a RegistryProxy for creating an object which delegates method calls to a registry object.
Application::dateTime() no longer relies on exceptions.
Added triggering to Registry, added Script object to encapsulate php scripts.
Improved array and file config classes.
Added dateTime() methods to Ergo.
Ergo::isStarted() returns false after Ergo::stop() again.
Ergo::stop() no longer destroys the application object.
Added a static counter for http requests via the client
Ergo_Error_WebErrorHandler context includes HTTP referer.
Ergo_Http_RequestFactory strips $_SERVER['REQUEST_URI'] down to a host-relative URL.
Prevented a redundant error from being written to the error log
Fixed a bug where log messages with % in them caused errors.
Errors in error proxy send http 500 status.

Fixed a bug where log levels were getting removed, added a process
logger that includes pid information.

Console error handler now only conditionally shows stack traces, added
more detailed exception logging.

StackTraceLogger now throws exceptions if it can't write to a log file,
the error handler handles these.

All errors are halting by default.

This is to make E_NOTICE's appear in a dev environment.
Changed calls to addLogger to addLoggers
Added Url->getUrlForParameters()
Added support for controller subdirectories to the controller locator

Refactored logging infrastructure to use a new interface for composite
logging and various other logging fixes.
WebErrorHandler sets headers to prevent HTTP caching of error responses.
New Ergo_Http_ResponseBuilder::notCachable() method.
Ergo_Http_ResponseBuilder::cacheControl() is chainable.
ErrorProxy doesn't fire shutdown hook if unregistered
Merge branch 'errorhandler-refactor'
Added a configurable timeout in the http client
Added a guard to check $_SERVER vars exist in the web error handler
Ergo_Application::errorProxy() public rather than private.
Updates to ErrorProxy and ErrorHandler.
Error Handlers do not exit on non-terminal errors such as notices.
Fixed setter behavior in Ergo_Application::genericFactory()

Fixed bug in the error proxy where error reporting level was being
ignored
Strange hack to fix method not exists errors
Added a logger class for interfacing with the linux syslog.

Refactored error handling infrastructure to technique for catching
uncatchable errors with a shutdown function, provided medium-specific
error handlers and a separate proxy object for interacting with PHP
error handling callbacks.
Added setter methods for Ergo methods.
Fixed a bug in getUrlFromPath method which wasn't splitting query strings correctly

Added an Ergo::request() method, along with a generic mechanism for
factory methods in the Application object and a lazy handle for Registry
entries.
Ergo_ErrorHandler respects error_reporting().
Updated errno to error string map in Ergo_ErrorHandler.
Ergo_Config_FileConfig::loadFile() is chainable.
New method: Ergo_Config_ArrayConfiguration::set()
Added Ergo::isStarted() static method.
Fixed fatal error: Attempt to unset static property Ergo::$_application
Fixed documented classnames in Ergo_Http_Client docblocks.
Ergo_Routing_RouteMapEntry exception message clarified.
Star matches in routes no match nothing, also fail on interpolation.

Added an addLoggers method for adding multiple loggers in one fell
swoop.
Added View package for composing simple view objects
Removed debugging output in Registry
Added a mixin class to promote composition
Allow addition of config files via the constructors in the FileConfig
Added a method to access logger factory
Added support for star routes in the routemap
Initial commit of ergo library, from 99designs commerce project
